EN: Every Christmas, our whole family gathers together to celebrate.

ZH: 这个周末，我们邀请了一些朋友来我们家聚在一起。
EN: This weekend, we invited some friends to gather together at our house.

ZH: 虽然大家各自忙着工作，但我们还是会经常聚在一起吃饭。
EN: Although everyone is busy with work, we still gather together for meals regularly.

